For the finaly Beast, we let 3 war tanks in defense (just to safe mana for the clerics - we do that with 4 clerics most of the time). As it is a medium long fight around 10to15mins with our dmg output, some necros help the cleric with a bit of mana. thats all. A nice fight with still great loots if you are not spoiled by VT or Elemetals.<br>
